images.prompt: A high-detail digital masterpiece depicting a regal woman shrouded in baroque elegance, her ethereal form illuminated by the flickering glow of ceremonial embers that cast warm, dynamic shadows across her intricate garments and flowing hair; her gaze is intense and contemplative as vibrating crystal rings orbit seamlessly around her, shimmering with life and energy, while the reverse tracking perspective amplifies the sense of depth and mystique, revealing the seamless blend of flame and steel tones in the richly textured background and foreground, evoking a surreal, timeless aura that merges ancient opulence with a futuristic aura, all rendered with hyper-realistic precision and cinematic finesse that immerses viewers into a vivid scene where history and mysticism intertwine in a luminous, vibrating tableau of celestial grace and ceremonial power.
